{{Noticebox/Official}}
The '''Chatbox''' lets you type messages to other users with a 144-character limit, and only the most recent message is visible. A typing indicator appears while you type. [[File:ChatboxAboveUser.png|thumb|Picture of a chatbox message]]

==Usage==

To open the chatbox, press <code>Y</code> if using a keyboard, or navigate to <code>[[Action Menu]] > Tools > Chatbox</code> for other input devices.

You can also send [[Open Sound Control|OSC]] data to the chatbox.

==Viewing and visuals==

By default, the chatbox is visible to everyone. You can change this in settings.

===Position===

After you send a message, it appears in one of two locations, depending on your chosen setting: 

* '''Above (Default)''': The message appears above the user who sent it
* '''Forward''': The message appears in front of the user who sent it

==Settings==

