==OSC==

While you can send OSC data to the chatbox, it also supports features not possible in the client, such as new lines, word wrap, disabling notification SFX, and more.

See the chatbox OSC docs [https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/osc-as-input-controller#chatbox here].

